Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The furthest space city from Earth,\Nknown as Side 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...proclaimed itself the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In roughly one month of fighting,\Nthe Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Federation Forces caused\Nthe deaths of half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vote to Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna II...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An asteroid placed in\Nthe moon's orbital path...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...to provide construction materials\Nfor the space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've made contact with Luna II...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can request permission to enter port\Nin my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant Wakkein will\Nhandle things from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must rest, sir.\NI'll get some painkillers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- We have canned food for you!\N- How many are in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for some hot water\Nto warm the milk earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- How long until we get to Luna II?\N- About one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\NWhen will the food rations come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you live\Nbefore coming to Side 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is my first time...\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Out in space, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're one of the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you being sarcastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to grow a tougher skin, Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take over for you.\NI just need to watch the gauges?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you could, until we dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Char's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Papua-class supply ship? Such an old ship\Ncan't carry all the supplies we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be realistic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't have the extra resources{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char, I sent two Zakus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get me the Federation's top secretssai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I requested three, but this is what I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we still don't know\Nthe full capabilities of their mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! He's in the Gundam's cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you food and fresh clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll start to stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're hardly eating, Amuro.\NYou've got to take time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so upset because of Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this because I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think Char's Musai\Nhasn't attacked us yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably still uncertain\Nof the White Base's capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They could have used up\Nall their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a ploy to make us think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship is approaching Char's Musai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure. They will dock in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just as Mirai said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't assume that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it's a battle cruiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they supply weapons\Nto Char's Musai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...we and Amuro\Nshould be able to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to launch an attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If Char strikes again, do you think\Nwe can survive, Mr. Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even have\None regular combatant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator! How long will it take the enemy\Nto transfer supplies between ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- If it's just weapons, then 10 minutes.\N- So we'd have a total of 25 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like your tone of voice. Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, however big the opponent may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...if he's wobbling or off-balance...\Nthen we can topple him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I learned in judo class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai! Get everyone on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency announcement!\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All combat-capable individuals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Irrespective of age...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Excluding engineers, all personnel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all supposed to go, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll wash these for you!\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to get everyone's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll decide by majority vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we only have a 50/50 chance\Nof pulling this off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but those who are in favor\Nof making a run for the Luna II base...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I count five votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, this is also a 50/50 chance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...those in favor of launching an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- We should fight!\N- Yeah! We should fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, it's decided then. We'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, to the Gundam.\NRyu, to the Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have to use the Guntank as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the beam cannons on standby.\NWhite Base, turn about 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Catapult connections complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, Core Fighter, okay to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Output, 60... 70...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...85... 120...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Fighter has been launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, prepare the Gundam for catapult.\NDo you know how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Catapult rig, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam output, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed for 10 km...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...and descend to approach enemy\Nfrom behind the ridge. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Roger!\N- Roger that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare port and starboard beam cannons,\Non the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by to fire!\NEnergy pipes connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward main cannon lifts, okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Loading commencing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have visual contact in 8 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, check your manuals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fire and give them cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't hit the Gundam\Nor the Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can such a tired old ship\Nremain in active service?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ensign Dren.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Open a video link with them.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The famous Red Comet wants supplies, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadem, the enemy's close. We must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that. think I'm that slow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm pretty swift for my age, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the hatches!\NHurry up and dock the conveyor pipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to receive conveyor pipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu's a soldier. He should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ascend? But the enemy's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize that we'll be\Nfacing the sun if we go in this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Musai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to see it any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That Amuro's pretty clever for a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he wants to attack\Nwith the sun behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Conveyor pipe docking, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin transfer of ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char! Don't you think this is odd?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know we're close to the enemy's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but It's located on the opposite side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Minovsky particle density{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, Gadem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- An enemy ship nearby?\N- It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I've got you now, Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Possible missile approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Impact in 3 seconds!\N3... 2... 1...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Conveyor pipes were hit!\NSeparate the ship from the Musai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Second missile approaching! 7... 6...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadem, release the Zakus you brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right! I'll do what I can!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,2... 1...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to deliver the Zakus to Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Matthew! Fix! Prepare to board the Zakus\Noutside of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll launch first in my mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch all our small missiles horizontally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dren, cover the Papua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is attacking with mobile suits,\Nnot battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn about 180 degrees, hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Blocks with remaining missiles,\Nfire everything you have toward the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How long until the mega particle cannons'\Nenergy is recharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 5 minutes, 20 seconds!\N- Damn! That's too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We reduced main engine power too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A third missile approaching!\N7... 6...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mobile suits are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming! Enemy fighter, port-stern!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Descend!\NWe'll drop the supplies on Luna II!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting strength isn't determined by\Ndifferences in mobile suit performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The bazooka's out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Commander Char! attacking us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Try to hold it off until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you hit our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have to keep Char occupied!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned Ryu!\NThanks to him, I can't fire the main cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, is it? Pass on the message...\N"Stay out of my way, Ryu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- But how do I contact the bridge...?\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Descend and turn about 170 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aim main cannons at enemy ship!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Musai's not attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't use their mega particle cannons\Nduring the resupply process. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...they have no missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Altitude 300!\NMusai descending to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Relative speed, 0.23 km/sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Estimated contact, 5.2 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Bright, I have a request.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Kai can't aim at the Musai.he way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, come in! Ryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- What happened?\N- His comm circuit isn't connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can't hit the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Inexperienced pilot! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! That Federation mobile suit\Nis a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- How can it withstand this beating...?!\N- Lt. Commander Char, please return!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't use ournons, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the Zakus?\NDo you have them yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Papua's catapult has been damaged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab the Zakus, even if that's all we get!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there! Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai says he has a special\Nlarge-vehicle license.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- His father is an engineer, so he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. He said a special license?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Don't we have\Na tank-type mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a two-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the main cannons on this ship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fire it. They taught me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to approach them in the Guntank?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! They're distracted\Nby the White Base, so we'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do it.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Musai will be taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the Zaku launch coming along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't repair the catapult!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! Push it out manually, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy recharge completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Prepare the mega particle cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking the Guntank so long?!\NFire on the enemy! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank is about to\Nleave the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground speed, 12.5 meters/sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,10 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai Shiden, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Head out in 3 seconds. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any choice, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Ms. Sayla, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste time with small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base, touchdown! Head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry, Mr. Kai!\NThe enemy is just over the ridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't yell! I'm having a hard enough time\Nmaking this thing run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Let's get this over with quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please proceed another 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely be within firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What If they fire missiles at us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're resupplying, so I doubt they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what If they do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. 10 more meters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Char's going to get his Zakus,\Nmissiles, and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a matter of honor\Nfor the supply corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Musai! You've got your Zakus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matthew! Fix! Get into the Zakus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned Red Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadem, what about the supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We dumped just about everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retrieve them after you defeat the enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?! The Federation's mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gadem, calm down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't stop me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They destroyed my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and my Zaku have fought in\Ncountless battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy the Federation's\Nslapped-together mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Gadem!\NYou can't do it with your Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You novice! You tried to attack too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the Federation developed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...a mobile suit like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gadem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retreat, Amuro! Retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've destroyed the supply ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't have weapons left either, do you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How are you going to fight Char?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papua's destroyed. Gadem's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear we lost because\Nthe Federation's new weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...are so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...what does it all mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Their military tactics are awkward,\Nand they fight like amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Commander!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Is Matthew and Fix In the Zakus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall we pursue the enemy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go cover the people loading the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir. Proceeding immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like they say, doing something\Nis better than worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You were only able to attack in the Guntank\Nbecause Amuro kept Char distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think it's true.\N- You brown-noser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Bright. Apparently\NI had the communications disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful next time.\NRemember your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to outflank the enemy too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No. His maneuver was sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Char was just too quick, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Char is also known as the Red Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought him once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Think a little more about your tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, take some rest while\Nmaintaining level 2 battle stations...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead on course to\Nthe Luna II front-line base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu. I have the feeling that,\NI'm gonna end up decking that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted.\NI brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Amuro! Good work, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sounding good, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I built it. It's called Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine field, 25 km to port.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Course, 3.2 to starboard.
